src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nPrinz max is the head of LGT &amp; the second son of the duke <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nThe family has a great rubens collection too<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T19:45:12.000Z","msg":"但如果用篇文嘅字眼「公國」<br />\n我唔太覺得係講緊列支？<br />\nLuxembourg 個政體係Grand Duchy  head of state係Duke<br />\nLiechtenstein係Principality  head of state係prince<br />\n當然都唔排除筆者寫錯/理解錯嘅<br />\n留名學嘢"},{"pid":"a3fc5956a84cb778dd38cf42a294416354c24d44","tid":2440180,"uid":17510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c16ff7c5f39467ea36a3e7823a8cd08ebbd542f2","tid":2440180,"uid":40216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8f2233c73653a266e014a1da2ca3521b8e8aaab6","tid":2440180,"uid":264974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T19:27:20.000Z","msg":"Liechtenstein?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T19:38:01.000Z","msg":"侯國來，得公爵F&uuml;rsten ，<br />\n嚴格來講只係貴族不算王室"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T22:18:58.000Z","msg":"侯國，係由邊一個皇帝封比佢？"},{"pid":"05a83e8d60eabd3ce42199e995a2e4c3473eded7","tid":2440180,"uid":40216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a3fc5956a84cb778dd38cf42a294416354c24d44","tid":2440180,"uid":17510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c16ff7c5f39467ea36a3e7823a8cd08ebbd542f2","tid":2440180,"uid":40216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8f2233c73653a266e014a1da2ca3521b8e8aaab6","tid":2440180,"uid":264974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T19:27:20.000Z","msg":"Liechtenstein?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T19:38:01.000Z","msg":"侯國來，得公爵F&uuml;rsten ，<br />\n嚴格來講只係貴族不算王室"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T22:18:58.000Z","msg":"侯國，係由邊一個皇帝封比佢？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T22:19:51.000Z","msg":"神聖羅馬帝國"},{"pid":"5bb8748e1f75735738e1640140fd8bd5d961ca09","tid":2440180,"uid":17510,"like":0,"dislik